ion error`, and handshake issues.\n   - Errors like `transport: Error while dialing` and `failed to get user cart during checkout` consistently point towards downstream system failures (e.g., cart service).\n\n2. **Checkoutservice Contextual Errors**:\n   - Checkoutservice occasionally logs warnings for `context canceled` related to order confirmations. Though these are less frequent, they hint at unstable communication.\n\n### Next Steps\n- Transition to deeper analysis on suspected components and impacted downstream systems (e.g., cart service and frontend dependencies).\n"}
